{
  "stem": "7337.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he went to the chief rabbi of France, who, incidentally, was Rabbi Kaplan.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He died last year.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he spent many years in a German concentration camp, after the French occupation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he asked the chief rabbi, where can we go?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the rabbi said, well, he'll think about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a few days later, he found us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said, I've just realized I've got family in South Africa.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, my father had never heard of South Africa.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I looked up the atlas, and I found Cape Town and Johannesburg.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I showed it to my dad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, do people live there?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, well, they must do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There-- there are towns there, so there must be some people living.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, we wrote to the-- no, we didn't write.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wrote to us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The relations of the rabbi wrote to us, and said that they came-- they would be coming to London shortly.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And why don't we come over to London and we can ask all the questions we'd like to-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] and they'd be happy to help us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we met them subsequently.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I think my father conversed with them in Yiddish, because he couldn't speak-- he couldn't speak English.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nor could I.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were some very helpful, very warm, well-known South African Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the long and the short is, as a result of that connection, we-- we decided to come to South Africa.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
